CREATE TABLE [cdc].[cdc_daily_cases]
( 
	[submission_date] [nvarchar](4000)  NULL,
	[state] [nvarchar](4000)  NULL,
	[tot_cases] [nvarchar](4000)  NULL,
	[new_case] [nvarchar](4000)  NULL,
	[pnew_case] [nvarchar](4000)  NULL,
	[tot_death] [nvarchar](4000)  NULL,
	[new_death] [nvarchar](4000)  NULL,
	[pnew_death] [nvarchar](4000)  NULL,
	[created_at] [nvarchar](4000)  NULL
)
WITH
(
	DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
	CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)
GO
